			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Making a Marsh out of a Mud Pile</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">In San Francisco Bay, scientists are looking for a better way to rebuild flagging marshland.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/erica-gies/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Erica Gies</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						April 10, 2024 | 900 words, about 4 minutes					</aside>
